{"word":"H8071 - שִׂמְלָה - simlâh - sim-law' - Apparel","slug":"H8071","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שִׂמְלָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>simlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sim-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Apparel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C2;&#x05DE;&#x05DC;&#x05D4; - s&#x0301;imla&#x0302;h</b> - <i>sim-law'</i><p/>Perhaps by permutation for the feminine of <a href=\"#/H5566\">H5566</a> (through the idea of a <i>cover</i> assuming the shape of the object beneath); a <i>dress</i>, especially a <i>mantle</i>: - apparel, cloth (-es, -ing), garment, raiment. Compare <a href=\"#/H8008\">H8008</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8008\">H8008</a>, <a href=\"#/H8072\">H8072</a>, <a href=\"#/H8079\">H8079</a>"}]}